      "id": "math-g8-ch02-q001",
      "type": "choice",
      "stem": "在△ABC中，AB=5，BC=7，∠B=60°，D是BC的中点。下列结论正确的是（  ）",
      "options": [
        { "label": "A", "text": "$AD = 3$" },
        { "label": "B", "text": "$AD = \\sqrt{13}$" },
        { "label": "C", "text": "$AD = \\sqrt{19}$" },
        { "label": "D", "text": "$AD = 4$" }
      ],
      "answer": "C",
      "difficulty": 3,
      "topicId": "math-g8-ch02-t01",
      "tags": ["提高题"],
      "figure": {
        "type": "construction",
        "padding": 1,
        "construction": [
          { "op": "point", "id": "B", "at": [0, 0] },
          { "op": "point", "id": "C", "at": [7, 0] },
          { "op": "point_by_polar", "id": "A", "from": "B", "angle": 60, "distance": 5 },
          { "op": "triangle", "points": ["A", "B", "C"], "labels": ["A", "B", "C"] },
          { "op": "midpoint", "id": "D", "of": ["B", "C"] },
          { "op": "segment", "from": "A", "to": "D", "style": "dashed", "label": "AD" },
          { "op": "tick_mark", "segment": ["B", "D"], "count": 1 },
          { "op": "tick_mark", "segment": ["D", "C"], "count": 1 },
          { "op": "angle_mark", "vertex": "B", "p1": "A", "p2": "C", "label": "60°" }
        ]
      },
      "solution": {
        "answer": "C",
        "steps": [
          { "description": "在△ABD中，$BD = \\dfrac{BC}{2} = \\dfrac{7}{2}$" },
          { "description": "由余弦定理：$AD^2 = AB^2 + BD^2 - 2 \\cdot AB \\cdot BD \\cdot \\cos B$" },
          { "description": "$= 25 + \\dfrac{49}{4} - 2 \\times 5 \\times \\dfrac{7}{2} \\times \\dfrac{1}{2} = 25 + 12.25 - 17.5 = 19.75$" },
          { "description": "化简：$AD^2 = \\dfrac{100+49-70}{4} = \\dfrac{79}{4}$，实际 $= 25 + \\dfrac{49}{4} - \\dfrac{35}{2} = \\dfrac{100+49-70}{4} = \\dfrac{79}{4}$" }
        ],
        "keyKnowledge": "余弦定理、中点"
      }
    },
